        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "样例 1：可以输入的字符串有 <code>aa</code>、<code>ab</code>、<code>ac</code>、<code>ba</code>、<code>bb</code>、<code>ca</code>、<code>cc</code>，共 $7$ 种。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "你的误区",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<em>(一开始的错误做法，容斥的对象不对)</em>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "你现在的做法是在对 <strong>字符集 (2^{26})</strong> 做容斥。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "虽然逻辑上也许能圆回来，但 $2^{26} \\approx 6.7 \\times 10^7$，而且你内部还有子集遍历或者其他逻辑，绝对会 <strong>TLE</strong>。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "正确的切入点",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "请看题目限制：$N \\leq 18$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这才是这道题的题眼！这在暗示你复杂度应该是 $O(2^{18})$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "你应该对 <strong>N 个字母集合</strong> 进行容斥，而不是对 26 个字母进行容斥。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "容斥模型推导",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们要算的是：所有行能打出的字符串集合的 <strong>并集</strong> 的大小。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "设 $A_i$ 是只用第 $i$ 行的按键能打出的长度为 $L$ 的字符串集合。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "答案是 $|\\bigcup_{i=1}^N A_i|$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "根据 <strong>容斥原理</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ |\\bigcup A_i| = \\sum |A_i| - \\sum |A_i \\cap A_j| + \\sum |A_i \\cap A_j \\cap A_k| - \\dots $$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>关键问题：</strong>$|A_i \\cap A_j|$ <strong>是什么？</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "交集 $A_i \\cap A_j$ 意味着字符串里的每一个字符，既要在 $S_i$ 里出现，也要在 $S_j$ 里出现。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "也就是说，可用字符集必须是 $S_i$ 和 $S_j$ 的 <strong>字符交集</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "假设 $S_i$ 和 $S_j$ 的公共字符有 $c$ 个，那么长度为 $L$ 的方案数就是 $c^L$。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "ll dp[N];\nbool vis[20][26];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n, L; cin >> n >> L;\n\tfa(i, 0, n - 1) {\n\t\tstring s; cin >> s;\n\t\tint cnt = 0;\n\t\tfor (char c : s)if (!vis[i][c - 'a']) {\n\t\t\tvis[i][c - 'a'] = 1;\n\t\t\tcnt++;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(k, 1, (1 << n) - 1) {\n\t\tint cnt = 0;\n\t\tvar mp = vector<int>(26);\n\t\tfa(i, 0, n - 1)if (k & (1 << i)) {\n\t\t\tfa(j, 0, 25)mp[j] += vis[i][j];\n\t\t}\n\t\tfa(i, 0, 25)cnt += (mp[i] == popcnt(k));\n\t\t\n\t\tdp[k] = Math::fastPow(cnt, L, mod);\n\t\tif (popcnt(k) & 1)ans = (ans + dp[k]) % mod;\n\t\telse ans = ((ans - dp[k]) % mod + mod) % mod;\n\t}\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
